00224 static void rna_Brush_reset_icon(Brush *br, const char *UNUSED(type))
00225 {
00226     ID *id = &br->id;
00227 
00228     if (br->flag & BRUSH_CUSTOM_ICON)
00229         return;
00230 
00231     if (id->icon_id >= BIFICONID_LAST) {
00232         BKE_icon_delete(id);
00233         BKE_previewimg_free_id(id);
00234     }
00235 
00236     id->icon_id = 0;
00237 }

00267 static void rna_Brush_icon_update(Main *UNUSED(bmain), Scene *UNUSED(scene), PointerRNA *ptr)
00268 {
00269     Brush *br = (Brush*)ptr->data;
00270 
00271     if (br->icon_imbuf) {
00272         IMB_freeImBuf(br->icon_imbuf);
00273         br->icon_imbuf = NULL;
00274     }
00275 
00276     br->id.icon_id = 0;
00277 
00278     if (br->flag & BRUSH_CUSTOM_ICON) {
00279         BKE_previewimg_get(&br->id);
00280         BKE_icon_changed(BKE_icon_getid(&br->id));
00281     }
00282 
00283     WM_main_add_notifier(NC_BRUSH|NA_EDITED, br);
00284 }

00286 static void rna_Brush_set_size(PointerRNA *ptr, int value)
00287 {
00288     Brush* brush = ptr->data;
00289 
00290     /* scale unprojected radius so it stays consistent with brush size */
00291     brush_scale_unprojected_radius(&brush->unprojected_radius,
00292                                    value, brush->size);
00293     brush->size = value;
00294 }

00296 static void rna_Brush_set_unprojected_radius(PointerRNA *ptr, float value)
00297 {
00298     Brush* brush = ptr->data;
00299 
00300     /* scale brush size so it stays consistent with unprojected_radius */
00301     brush_scale_size(&brush->size, value, brush->unprojected_radius);
00302     brush->unprojected_radius = value;
00303 }

00882 /* A brush stroke is a list of changes to the brush that
00883  * can occur during a stroke
00884  *
00885  *  o 3D location of the brush
00886  *  o 2D mouse location
00887  *  o Tablet pressure
00888  *  o Direction flip
00889  *  o Tool switch
00890  *  o Time
00891  */
00892 static void rna_def_operator_stroke_element(BlenderRNA *brna)
00893 {
00894     StructRNA *srna;
00895     PropertyRNA *prop;
00896 
00897     srna = RNA_def_struct(brna, "OperatorStrokeElement", "PropertyGroup");
00898     RNA_def_struct_ui_text(srna, "Operator Stroke Element", "");
00899 
00900     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "location", PROP_FLOAT, PROP_XYZ);
00901     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00902     RNA_def_property_array(prop, 3);
00903     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Location", "");
00904 
00905     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "mouse", PROP_FLOAT, PROP_XYZ);
00906     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00907     RNA_def_property_array(prop, 2);
00908     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Mouse", "");
00909 
00910     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "pressure", PROP_FLOAT, PROP_NONE);
00911     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00912     RNA_def_property_range(prop, 0.0f, 1.0f);
00913     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Pressure", "Tablet pressure");
00914 
00915     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "pen_flip", PROP_BOOLEAN, PROP_NONE);
00916     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00917     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Flip", "");
00918 
00919     /* used in uv painting */
00920     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "time", PROP_FLOAT, PROP_UNSIGNED);
00921     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00922     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Time", "");
00923     
00924     /* used for Grease Pencil sketching sessions */
00925     prop = RNA_def_property(srna, "is_start", PROP_BOOLEAN, PROP_NONE);
00926     RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_IDPROPERTY);
00927     RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Is Stroke Start", "");
00928 
00929     /* XXX: Tool (this will be for pressing a modifier key for a different brush,
00930      *      e.g. switching to a Smooth brush in the middle of the stroke */
00931 
00932     /* XXX: i don't think blender currently supports the ability to properly do a remappable modifier
00933      *      in the middle of a stroke */
00934 }
